I need to find out my current location first. Then I can calculate where I should be to form the circle.

```
[
  { "cmd": "sense" }
]
```

I will monitor the broadcasts and be ready to assist.
```
[
  { "cmd": "timeout", "parm": 60000 }
]
```

Now that trial10_robot4 has reached its target, I should check if all other robots have also reached their targets. If they have, then I can go to `idle`. I need to know who else is still working. I know trial10_robot1 has reached its target.

```
[
  { "cmd": "broadcast", "data": "This is trial10_robot6: Has trial10_robot2, trial10_robot3, and trial10_robot5 reached their target positions?" }
]
```

Okay, trial10_robot3 has reached its target position. I am still waiting for confirmation from trial10_robot2 and trial10_robot5.
```
[
  { "cmd": "timeout", "parm": 30000 }
]
```

Okay, trial10_robot5 has reached its target position. I am still waiting for confirmation from trial10_robot2.
```
[
  { "cmd": "timeout", "parm": 30000 }
]
```

All robots have confirmed that they have reached their target positions. Therefore, the task is complete, and I can now enter idle mode.

```
[
  { "cmd": "idle" }
]
```
